snippet.title: Vintage WIN - Undersea Adventure (1995)
snippet.description:
This along with 3D Dinosaur Adventure and 3D Body Adventure came together in a 3-CD set I got as a kid. This was my 2nd favorite game of the 3 (the first being the dinosaurs of course)


Undersea Adventure was released by KA in 1995 as a CD Version with voice speech and mini-games. I am not sure if there was a floppy version predecessor.
